The paper discusses the use of honeynets as a cyber defense mechanism, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also applies reinforcement learning to solve the Semi-Markov Decision Process (SMDP), which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the implementation costs and risks of honeynets, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
